HEADWORD: Inducteous
<hw>In*duc"te*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Elec.)</fld>
<def>Rendered electro-polar by induction, or brought into the opposite
electrical state by the influence of inductive bodies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inductile</ent>⟦br⟧
